{"lemma":"خَتْمُ","slug":"خَتْمُ","root":"خ.ت.م","root_slug":"خ-ت-م","root_link":"/words/roots/خ-ت-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"خَتْمُ","root":"ختم","pos":"V","occurrence_count":5},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n10002","n10003"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AE%D9%8E%D8%AA%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to seal","examples":[{"text":"خَتَمَ ٱللَّهُ عَلَىٰ قُلُوبِهِمْ وَعَلَىٰ سَمْعِهِمْ وَعَلَىٰٓ أَبْصَـٰرِهِمْ غِشَـٰوَةٌ وَلَهُمْ عَذَابٌ عَظِيمٌ","english":"Allah has sealed their hearts and their hearing, and their sight is covered. They will suffer a tremendous punishment."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to seal, stamp","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to put a signet-ring on someone's finger","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stamping, sealing","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"stamp, seal","tags":["obsolete"],"examples":[{"text":"خَتْمٌ مَطَّاطِيٌّ","english":"rubber stamp"},{"text":"خَتْمُ ٱلْمُوَافَقَةِ","english":"seal of approval"}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root خ ت م (ḵ t m). Compare Egyptian ḫtm (“to seal”), Hebrew חתם (ħatám)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n10002","headword_ar":"خَتْمٌ","root":"xtm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"inf. n. of 1 [q. v.]. (S, Mgh, Msb, K.)       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"impress produced by the engraving of a signet."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoTaAniY xatomiY","text_ar":"اَعْطَانِى خَتْمِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave me my sufficiency,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what sufficed me:"},{"kind":"text","text":"because what suffices a man is the last [or utmost] of his desire, or demand. (TA.)       -A3-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Honey."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b2-  And (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"orifices of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xalaAyaA","text_ar":"خَلَايَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hives"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of bees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n10003","headword_ar":"خَتَمٌ","root":"xtm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAtamN","text_ar":"خَاتَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sealed piece of clay"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wax"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafaDN","text_ar":"نَفَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manofuwDN","text_ar":"مَنْفُوضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qabaDN","text_ar":"قَبَضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maqobuwDN","text_ar":"مَقْبُوضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so in the saying of El-Aashà,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"wa A^aborazahaA wa EalayohaA xatamo \n                      \n                     \n                        wa SaHobaA='a TaAfa yahuwdiy~uhaA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And"},{"kind":"text","text":"a jar of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reddish-coloured"},{"kind":"text","text":"wine,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Jew"},{"kind":"text","text":"-vender"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereof came, and brought it out, with a sealed piece of clay upon it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_b